column5: What another awesome day i had fishing with my son we did not fish in the kayak or canoe but we back packed into a lake i love fishing and used a boat the heat and the bugs were crazy and it was time to give my son some of my fishing tricks as i don't get to fish with him lots because of his work hours.
Very nice specs. Welcome to the board, I'm familiar with some of your exploits from another forum and I think the members here will enjoy your contributions.
Super awesome! Very nice outing, and great catches !! If you can please post the gps Co-ordinates, I’m sure a few million fisherman would be happy to ruin the spot for you.
Beauty. Love to see these kind of reports
Thanks guys i enjoy making videos and posting pics.I will also post my 2 daýs from the end of May .
Those are some chunky specs, thanks for posting ....
Can you please adopt me? Pretty please?  S.
Wow. Beautiful fish. I love lakes like that. The bugs are totally worth it.
